text: Eliasz Kuziemski (30 July 1922 - 1 June 2000) was a Polish actor. He appeared in more than 50 films and television shows between 1956 and 1989. ==Selected filmography== * Katastrofa (1965) * Stawka większa niż życie (1967) ==References== ==External links== * Category:1922 births Category:2000 deaths Category:Polish male film actors
